@startuml Sequence_Candidate_Notifications
title Ứng Viên - Quản Lý Thông Báo (Module D)

actor Candidate as "👤 Ứng viên"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant NotificationService as "Notification\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Xem Danh Sách Thông Báo ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Thông báo"
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: GET /api/notifications?page=0&size=20
NotificationService -> Database: Query thong_bao (candidateId)
Database --> NotificationService: Return notifications
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: Notifications list
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị danh sách thông báo

== Xem Chi Tiết Thông Báo ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click vào 1 thông báo
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: GET /api/notifications/{notificationId}
NotificationService -> Database: Get thong_bao details
Database --> NotificationService: Notification details
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: Full notification info
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị chi tiết thông báo

== Đánh Dấu Đã Xem ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click notification
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: PATCH /api/notifications/{notificationId}/read
NotificationService -> Database: Update isRead = true
Database --> NotificationService: OK
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: Marked as read
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Notification gray out (no longer bold)

== Đánh Dấu Tất Cả Đã Xem ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Đánh dấu đã xem tất cả"
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: PATCH /api/notifications/mark-all-read
NotificationService -> Database: Update all isRead = true (for candidateId)
Database --> NotificationService: OK
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: All marked as read
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ Tất cả thông báo đã xem

== Xem Số Thông Báo Chưa Xem ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: (on header/badge)
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: GET /api/notifications/unread-count
NotificationService -> Database: Count unread notifications
Database --> NotificationService: Unread count (5)
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: Unread count
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Show badge: "5" (red circle)

== Cài Đặt Thông Báo ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Cài đặt thông báo"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show preferences
Candidate -> FrontEnd: Toggle: ứng tuyển / phỏng vấn / offer
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Save preferences

@enduml
